description: Per-report 1:1 workspace for managers — recurring agenda, running notes timeline, open action items, goals tracker, and feedback log — so every 1:1 is prepared and nothing important gets lost in scattered Docs. Keeps your HRIS and Calendar as the system of record and replaces the Notion pages nobody updates between sessions.
